Popular Limpopo Musician King Monada is working with Skeem Saam Actor, Clement Maosa, on a new song. This collaboration will mark Clements first music project! King Monada retweeted the video “This is what I do when I don’t make my own music . I do some sound mixing and I later on do mastering ! That’s a song by @KingMonada_ & @clementmaosa .Dropping by September” The Ska Bora Moreki hitmaker and Clement have an established relationship. Clement was featured as the protagonist on King Monada’s latest music video for the single, Motho Kadi Bag, which was released on Thursday, 25 July 2019. Watch the video sample of King Monada and Clement Maosa’s single below:  